Transcription.Text: There it was developed into quite an elaborate and distinctive form with rosettes, leaves and lace fillings. During the time of Victoria this gentle craft was greatly abused. It was some years after the Victorian period that designers realised the potentialities of the craft, and crochet was revived with designs suitable for contemporary trends.
